<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Suggestion Approved</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        .header,
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .header img {
            max-width: 100px;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
        }
        .regards {
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        .regards p {
            margin: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hello <%= studioName %>,</h2>

            <p>A suggestion for your studio has been approved. Here are the details:</p>

            <h3>Suggestion Details:</h3>
            <p><strong>User Name:</strong> <%= user_name %></p>
            <p><strong>Suggestion:</strong> <%= suggested_text %></p>

            <p>We have reviewed and approved the user's suggestion for your studio.</p>

            <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact us.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="regards">
            <p><strong>Best regards,</strong><br>Our Team</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>
                For support, please contact:
                <a href="mailto:support@thai-massage.de">support@thai-massage.de</a>
            </p>
            <p>
                &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Thai-Massage.de. All rights
                reserved.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
